### Infrastructure Checks
### Run these to verify the setup is correct before testing the full API.

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 🩺  Health & Infrastructure
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Database + API health check
### ✅ Expected: 200 {"status":"Healthy"}
GET https://localhost:7000/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Swagger UI available in dev
### ✅ Expected: 200 with Swagger HTML
GET https://localhost:7000/swagger
Accept: text/html

###

### Root redirect — should redirect to /swagger
GET https://localhost:7000/
Accept: application/json

